title: Elliptical Workout in 15 min
description:
Have you been sitting at your desk or lounging on the sofa all day long? A little movement will do your body good, and this easy 15-minute elliptical workout is the perfect way to get it in today. Sunny Trainer Brittany is the best companion to bring along for the ride!

Workout Length: 15-Minute
Workout Level: Any Level
Products Used:  Premium Cardio Climber Machine SF-E3919
Trainer: Brittany Noelle

✨ Workout Details ✨
0:00 | Intro

Light consistent pace – enjoy some beautiful visualization of the beach while you take it easy! 

END OF WORKOUT
